## --- Visual Studio Build Outputs ---
# WPFのbinとobjフォルダを完全に除外
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

# WPF / .NET Publish Profiles
**/Properties/PublishProfiles/*.pubxml

## --- .NET / Visual Studio User Files ---
# ユーザー固有の設定やキャッシュ
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## --- IDE Tools and Cache ---
# Visual Studioが生成するキャッシュフォルダ
.vs/

## --- Rider / Resharper (もし他のIDEを使う場合) ---
.idea/
*.sln.DotSettings.user
